name: EKCalendarChooserDelegate
desc: Methods a calendar chooser's delegate may use to receive notifications.

items.name: func calendarChooserDidFinish(EKCalendarChooser)
items.desc: Sent when a user selects one or more calendars.

items.name: func calendarChooserSelectionDidChange(EKCalendarChooser)
items.desc: Sent when a user changes the selection.

items.name: func calendarChooserDidCancel(EKCalendarChooser)
items.desc: Sent when the user cancels a calendar selection.
